Z","msg":"睇字都見到佢哋好'pure' 好 'sweet' <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n『由於戶主夫婦一直很想到希臘地方，但尚未有機會前往，所以特別放大愛琴海相片於客廳，提醒自己一定要去一敞愛琴海』<br />\n<br />\n『由於他不懂鋼琴，為了表演他特意秘密練兵，自己找導師學琴，然後表演一首曲，可是最終都是彈不出來。』<br />\n<br />\n『洗碗機是世上最偉大的發明，因為有了這部機，她與丈夫為洗碗而爭相推讓，又可以洗得更乾淨。』<br />\n<br />\n『男戶主表示，他對廚房基本上沒有要求，唯一最希望有一部焗爐，他又指，其實每年都只有一次會入廚房，就是老婆生日前夕，他就會焗一個蛋糕，給老婆做生日禮物。』"},{"pid":"9dc20bdce59c25bbf4602970b30345b9237315f7","tid":2516353,"uid":80314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6984aa2990b7b52fe1b37b388b66c042a08c847e","tid":2516353,"uid":80314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:54:04.000Z","msg":"睇字都見到佢哋好'pure' 好 'sweet' <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n『由於戶主夫婦一直很想到希臘地方，但尚未有機會前往，所以特別放大愛琴海相片於客廳，提醒自己一定要去一敞愛琴海』<br />\n<br />\n『由於他不懂鋼琴，為了表演他特意秘密練兵，自己找導師學琴，然後表演一首曲，可是最終都是彈不出來。』<br />\n<br />\n『洗碗機是世上最偉大的發明，因為有了這部機，她與丈夫為洗碗而爭相推讓，又可以洗得更乾淨。』<br />\n<br />\n『男戶主表示，他對廚房基本上沒有要求，唯一最希望有一部焗爐，他又指，其實每年都只有一次會入廚房，就是老婆生日前夕，他就會焗一個蛋糕，給老婆做生日禮物。』"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:54:28.000Z","msg":"re錯<br />\n<br />\ndiu"},{"pid":"064106c79a1eb16bd8de881f26c5df52cf8d5f6b","tid":2516353,"uid":240670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T04:18:41.000Z","msg":"太平<br />\n<br />\n下個月就上到800萬<br />\n+請假鬥快買+出多幾萬求業主賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓市gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac66f6d2c3b410fc6e6e6c68b6cf4e3fb219cdb5","tid":2516353,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87e0b4e5a1428b91d95d379d18d24ccbd948d201","tid":2516353,"uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59c43808814b11b16b748d232d3af10e8ba8e54c","tid":2516353,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T16:02:54.000Z","msg":"好近地鐵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:42:27.000Z","msg":"5分鐘步程"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T04:19:11.000Z","msg":"行公園條路好好行"},{"pid":"5cbee19ce996ec6c642997415cc6a13f336f4b9f","tid":2516353,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac66f6d2c3b410fc6e6e6c68b6cf4e3fb219cdb5","tid":2516353,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87e0b4e5a1428b91d95d379d18d24ccbd948d201","tid":2516353,"uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59c43808814b11b16b748d232d3af10e8ba8e54c","tid":2516353,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T16:02:54.000Z","msg":"好近地鐵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:42:27.000Z","msg":"5分鐘步程"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T04:19:11.000Z","msg":"行公園條路好好行"},"citedBy":0,"reply